Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.10,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.81,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.98,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:18.11,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.88,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:39.30,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:51.19,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.44,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:57.24,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:02.12,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:07.58,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:16.88,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:22.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:28.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were another\N23 victims yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:31.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we began to suspect\Nthat Kira was a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:34.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the timing of the killings changed as\Nif to contradict our theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:37.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that Kira knows\Nwhat the police know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When L discovers that the findings\Nfrom the investigation were leaked,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:44.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he's bound to search for leads on me\Nwithin the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:48.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's been following you\Nall this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, I'll be sure to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a Shinigami's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:01.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a human's name and life span\Ncan be seen above person's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:06.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami can also turn the eyes\Nof whoever picked up their Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:09.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,into Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:16.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes\Nis half of that person's remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, what'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Ryuk around lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really lose his Death Note\Nin the Human World?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note was probably picked up\Nby a human before he got to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happened to him, he'd have to\Nfollow that person around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until that person dies\Nor the Death Note is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:41.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't picture Ryuk\Ndoing something so tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:48.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he was\Ncarrying two Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?\NWhy would he need two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand\Nwhat he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for me to gain\Nthe eyes of a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to offer half of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:04.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna make\Na deal with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This deal...\Nis out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:33.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to create an ideal,\Nnew world free from criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also intend to reign as\Nthe god in that world for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would consider the deal if\Nit lengthened my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not worth talking\Nabout if it's going to shorten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You, of all people,\Nshould know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:50.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just felt I should tell\Nyou a deal like this exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:55.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to complain that\NI didn't tell you about this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't tell me\Nabout this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're too late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me this\Nwhen we first met
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:07.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or included this when you were writing\Ninstructions in the Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he's not frightened nor\Ndoes he try to suck up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no problem giving me\Na hard time about things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:24.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure there isn't anything else you\Nwant to tell me ahead of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?\NHow disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have seriously\Nconsidered the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you offered me wings\Nrather than eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:46.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying around freely in the sky\Nis very God-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:50.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream that man\Nhas had since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd stand out if you sprouted\Nwings and started flying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bet you'd get arrested\Nby the police just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, that was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:04.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if I continue to\Ndeal for eyes and wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to end up becoming\Na real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be amusing,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without all that,\Nyou're already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a worthy Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami Realm is\Nrotting these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:27.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all live vacant lives\Nand only take human lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because they don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one even knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why we exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt there's any reason\Nat all for our existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:45.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much more of\Na Shinigami than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:50.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, from what you're saying, it sounds\Nlike I'm doing a lot more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to be lumped together\Nwith the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:58.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am using this Death Note\Nas a human for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:06.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I wouldn't say that the Shinigami Realm\Nis meaningless to humans either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever a Shinigami like you\Ncomes to the Human World
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,once every hundred, no,\Nevery thousand years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Human World\Nchanges greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:22.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami Realm's existence\Nis fearfully meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-ls that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that the\NShinigami Realm is rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you return\Nfrom this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how about using what you've\Nlearned here to try to change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:39.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...you may be\Nquite the positive thinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't, I wouldn't be\Ntrying to use
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Death Note to try to\Nmake the world a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?\NWhat did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:04.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How to find out the name of\Nthe guy who was following me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use the rules of\Nthe Death Note to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I write a cause of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an additional\N6 minutes and 40 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:15.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to record specific conditions\Nand time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:20.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how free I can\Nbe with these conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.83,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}The Following Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another six inmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart attacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:36.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:38.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three exhibited bizarre behavior\Nbefore they died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't just die from\Nsimple heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:51.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they died of heart attacks,\Nbut before one of them died...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:54.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he drew a strange picture\Non the wall with blood from his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another left a letter that doesn't seem\Nlike a will or anything meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:03.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The third escaped just to go\Nto the employees' bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:16.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More victims, but their circumstances\Nare unlike those we've had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike those before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall send you an image of\Nthe picture and letter left at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A note describing a fear of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:33.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This can be taken as\Nsomething a criminal might do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira can control the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can control actions\Nright before death as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that would mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about these current victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the media know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,aside from the fact that\Nthey died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:57.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that Kira\Nwas performing some kind of test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:02.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we'd only\Nbe giving him the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Performing tests on criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's playing with peoples' lives\Nas if this is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is using criminals\Nas test subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he trying to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:37.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The results of yesterday's test have\Nalready been input into Dad's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:42.14,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.896\pos(306,233)}Keito Nawarami: Kidnapping Murder
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:42.14,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.896\pos(338,362)}Kyu Nishida: Insurance Fraud Murder
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The results are just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note will work\Nfor what I have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:48.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to the bathroom\NI had designated in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:57.35,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz346.61\move(175,137,179,180,0,9143)}Tamiki: Heart attack,\N\Nescapes from cell.\N\NDies 6 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:57.35,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz341.091\move(135,316,143,355,0,9143)}Masaaki: Heart attack,\N\N\Ndraws symbol on wall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:52.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another drew the same picture\NI had drawn in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:57.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another wrote the same letter\NI had written in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.36,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(515,229)\frz15.895}Lord have mercy\NDo what I can,\NI'll either be\Nhanged or you\Nknow it, killed\Nby Kira. I know\Nabout him. He's\N going to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These three did exactly what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I purposely wrote very difficult tasks\Nfor the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.96,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(462,209)\frz14.662\fad(542,500)}Yuzo Fura: Dies\N\N\Nin front of the\N\N\NEiffel Tower France,\N\N\Ntoday at 6 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first was to "Die in front of the\NEiffel Tower in an hour."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:17.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's physically impossible to go from\Na prison in Japan to France in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this never happened and ended\Nas just a regular heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:27.44,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz349.3\pos(133,178)}Kabeoka: Heart Attack\N\NDraws exact image\N\Nof L's face on prison wall\N\NDies at 6 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:27.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The next was to "draw a picture of L's face\Non the prison wall," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One can't draw the faces...\Nof people they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:40.57,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz348.516\move(388,128,336,128,0,8503)}Kabeoka: Heart Attack\NDraws exact image of\NL's face on prison wall\NDies at 6 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:40.57,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz346.018\move(334,328,280,321,0,8503)}Shinshiro Yamamae: Heart Attack\NWrites a note stating "I know that L is\Nsuspicious of the Japanese police."\NDies at 6 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the final one,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I specified that he would write...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:40.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dies at 6 p.m.\Na note that would read, "I know L is\Nsuspicious of the Japanese police."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this one might work,\Nbut it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that people can't write
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:52.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about things they don't know or things\Nthey couldn't come up with on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:57.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it means that even the\NDeath Note can't do the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as it's something\Nthe person is realistically likely to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can control them as much as\NI want before he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've figured that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:10.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you trying to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:14.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L and the police will never\Nfigure out my true goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The great detective\Nis probably trying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:21.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to decipher the picture and\Nthe letter those criminals left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an absolutely\Nmeaningless dying message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:32.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira used those criminals for a test,\Nhe's about to start something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:37.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he moves now,\Nthere is the chance that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the FBI will notice someone\Nacting suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:44.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he has a different goal in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the letter and picture might\Nbe some kind of message...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:50.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.94,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,460)}L  D O  Y O U  K N O W
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's time for the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a drug addict who tried\Nto rob a bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.41,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6.599\move(346,157,362,418,0,3577)}Wanted Criminal\NKiichiro Osoreda
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but wasn't able to steal any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked civilians and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's last minute, but I'm sure\NI can find someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to ask out several people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask out...several people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:13.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:18.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, I may not look it,\Nbut I'm pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:32.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Huh, Light?\NGood morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still following me, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:57.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't have my stalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be no point in what\NI'm going to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- A date?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a date,\Nno matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even to my stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no normal date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you found a way\Nto find out your stalker's name, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:31.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ryuk, didn't you see\Nwhat I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:34.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. It would be boring to peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just be patient and\Nwatch what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I haven't been to\NSpace Land since junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!\NAnd I get to be alone with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On weekdays, he only goes\Nto school and his prep courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An occasional date on his days off.\NHe's pretty normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's a serious\Nhigh school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Yagami's son, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:17.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish my surveillance\Nof him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you weren't going out\Nuntil entrance exams were over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I did score number one\Nin the practice exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:31.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from him,\Nthere are seven passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:18.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking control of this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus jacking!\NAt a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:30.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss!\NI'll kill anyone that moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:35.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Driver, you know the phone number\Nfor Space Land's offices, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:36.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is Sasaki, the driver of\Nbus number 174!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man with a gun has\Nbus jacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that? Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Space Land's profits from yesterday\Nto two bus stops away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a woman bring it\Nby car alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it before this bus gets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try anything funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:06.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or call the police,\NI'll kill all the passengers one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for the chance to grab his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that's holding the pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous. Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to that, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NWe don't have to pass notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:32.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we whisper, he won't hear us\Nover the sound of the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:38.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have proof that\Nyou're not his accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty common.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit pretends he's alone\Nand just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:49.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll leave someone to\Nkeep watch in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...you really think so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:56.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that\NLight Yagami can be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira could kill the culprit\Nwith a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my proof.\NTake a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:07.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,FBI?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:14.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, L's using the FBI to investigate\Nthose connected to Japan's police force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is...\NRaye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:26.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask why an FBI agent\Nis on this bus with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you have a gun?\N- Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So if something happens,\NI can rely on you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That man was on the\NJapanese news two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a drug addict who tried\Nto rob a bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,killed three civilians,\Nand ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:53.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all right.\NHe'll never shoot at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:06.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were planning something back here\Nwith notes, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees that note from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll discover that Light was planning\Nto jump him when he had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:17.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh. Plans for a date?\NHow stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:20.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:35.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You in the back?\NW-What are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How long were you\Nhiding back there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:44.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean me?\NYou can see me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll shoot!\NYou monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:50.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!\NHe's hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:19:00.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!\NThat note that Light just dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was cut out of the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:09.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he has this guy touch the note\Nand now, only he can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:10.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Shinigami,\Nso that's not gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anyone who touches the Death Note\Nwill be able to see me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm always hovering behind you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinigami can't die from gunshots..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all stuff I've told Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty impressive,\Nhe used his skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not surprising he's the\Ntop exam scorer nationwide...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:53.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He even used this bus jacking to get the\Nname of the guy who was following him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without much hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the bus and open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Space Land
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly 11:45.\NEverything went as planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted Criminal\NKiichiro Osoreda, Accidental death...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:40.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At 11:31 a.m., he will get on\Na bus heading to Space Land
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from the bus stop near\Nthe eastern entrance of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He will enter with a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:50.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but will see a phantom from another\Nworld and fires all his bullets at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he will flee from the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:58.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately afterwards, at 11:45\Nthe same day, he will die in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next, Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:27.84,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:33.22,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:42.23,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:48.65,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:53.20,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:58.91,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:06.38,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:11.55,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:22.31,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:28.11,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:38.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't suspected me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:37.49,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(312,343)}Please keep what is about to happen\Na secret between the eight of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:42.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining agents will\Nall die of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Raye Penber.
